msIdentifier.repository: Rampur Raza Library (रामपुर रज़ा किताब ख़ाना) , Rampur

summary.p: 345 fol.; Writing surface: parchment; Shelfmark: No.1; Lines per page: 15-16; Dimensions: 287 x 202 mm; Qurʾānic Text: Q 1:1-7, Q 2:21-40, Q 2:82-218, Q 2:221-279, Q 2:281- Q 3:51, Q 3:53-Q 17:7, Q 17:15-Q 42:51, Q 43:19-Q 50:38, Q 51:57- Q 65:6, Q 67- Q 74:41, Q 91:4- Q 106:0, Q 111- Q 114:5; Script style: kūfī C.III; Estimated date of production: 700-850. Unfortunately, images of folios 7v, 8r are 336v are missing in this entry.

THe catalogue of Arabic manuscripts of the Rampur library gives the following information (Arshi 1963, p. 2-3): "S. No & Subject: 1 E. al-Qurʾān, Accn.No.: 24536 D.; Titel of Work: al-Qurʾānuʾl-Maǧīd; Material: Parchment; Script: ʿAr. (Kūfī); Size, folios & lines per page: S. 28,7x20,2; F. 343 x 7 = 350; L. 15-6; Extent: Inc. Several Foll. missing.; Condition and age: Good 1st/7th Cent.; Additional Particulars: A priceless copy ascribed to the penmanship of Amīruʾl-Muʾminīn ʿAlī b. Abī Ṭālib al-Qurashī al-Hāshimī (d. 40/661). With modern gold & coloured borders on paper margins. Red dots used instead of diacritical marks.
